purpose "Reconstructor for DirC.

By Wilka Carvalho <wcarvalho92@gmail.com>"

# Options
option "new" n "runs all programs before it, i.e generator, simulator" optional
option "verbose" v "print data" optional
option "event" e "print data for specific event (starting at 0th event)" int optional
option "last" l "only reconstructs the last l particles" int optional
option "modified-particle-info" m "output file for modified particle information i.e removing some particles to only track the remaining" string optional